WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.500 --> 00:00:02.300
Master, you actually doubt me

2
00:00:02.666 --> 00:00:04.533
How could I possibly do such a thing?

3
00:00:04.533 --> 00:00:07.900
Is it not that you are wronged, master?

4
00:00:07.933 --> 00:00:09.800
I am loyal to you

5
00:00:09.866 --> 00:00:11.766
Besides, Yuanbao is your own flesh and blood

6
00:00:11.766 --> 00:00:13.866
How could I possibly do such a thing?

7
00:00:14.100 --> 00:00:15.766
It's really not me.

8
00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:21.466
What else do you want to say now?

9
00:00:21.466 --> 00:00:23.466
From the moment you entered the door, I realized that you were not normal

10
00:00:23.466 --> 00:00:24.400
Hovering left and right

11
00:00:24.400 --> 00:00:26.166
In fact, that location is a surveillance dead end.

12
00:00:26.166 --> 00:00:27.566
And you are also careful

13
00:00:27.566 --> 00:00:28.800
But you don't know.

14
00:00:28.800 --> 00:00:29.966
This hotel

15
00:00:30.333 --> 00:00:31.866
Under Genting Group

16
00:00:31.933 --> 00:00:33.933
I will not allow this to happen.

17
00:00:33.933 --> 00:00:35.400
So I'm in every corner

18
00:00:35.400 --> 00:00:37.266
They have hidden cameras installed

19
00:00:37.266 --> 00:00:39.466
I'm just helping the hotel staff

20
00:00:39.466 --> 00:00:41.166
Sprinkle some powdered sugar on top of the cake

21
00:00:41.166 --> 00:00:42.333
To make that cake

22
00:00:42.333 --> 00:00:43.833
It looks a little bit more appealing.

23
00:00:43.900 --> 00:00:44.866
Shilin Mundi

24
00:00:44.933 --> 00:00:47.166
That cake was eaten by Lin Mengdi for the ingot

25
00:00:47.166 --> 00:00:49.233
He must have got poison powder on his fingers

26
00:00:49.300 --> 00:00:51.066
Otherwise, why are the other guests okay?

27
00:00:51.066 --> 00:00:53.766
No one has eaten cake since we entered

28
00:00:53.766 --> 00:00:54.133
and

29
00:00:54.133 --> 00:00:56.966
You were before Lin Mengdi brought the cake to the ingot

30
00:00:57.766 --> 00:00:59.400
You took advantage of everyone's attention

31
00:00:59.400 --> 00:01:01.066
It's all on me and ingot

32
00:01:01.066 --> 00:01:02.966
I slowly approached the cake stand

33
00:01:03.100 --> 00:01:04.033
and

34
00:01:04.333 --> 00:01:07.600
The tissue next to the cake still smells of your perfume

35
00:01:08.766 --> 00:01:10.166
This perfume is only for you.

36
00:01:10.166 --> 00:01:12.200
Said it wasn't you

37
00:01:13.533 --> 00:01:14.933
I sprinkled poison powder

38
00:01:14.933 --> 00:01:16.366
It's a waste of me being so sincere

39
00:01:16.366 --> 00:01:17.500
But the master

40
00:01:17.533 --> 00:01:19.200
I have a reason

